/WEAPONABILITY STR WEAPONABILITY/
/WEAPONTAGS WEAPONTAGS/
/WEAPONRANGE 1 WEAPONRANGE/
/WEAPONHANDS 2 WEAPONHANDS/
/WEAPONDAMAGE 4 WEAPONDAMAGE/
/WEAPONDESCRIPTION
This is the largest of swords, a fully two-handed weapon. It is heavy enough to damage an opponent by sheer force, but also sharp and quick like any other sword. 
These weapons are bulky and quite inconvenient to carry around and are normally relegated to situations where a character expects heavy fighting.
WEAPONDESCRIPTION/
WEAPON/
/WEAPON /ID" b4815920-6712-11ee-98db-c87f5455cfcc"/
