sizes, but they all have some things in common, a handle and a weighted head with a sharp edge. This kind of weapon is particularly favored by woodsmen and less affluent 
warriors as it is cheap, fairly easy to make, and effective.
WEAPONDESCRIPTION/
WEAPON/
