/IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION
Since ancient times wise men have wielded staves of enormous magical potency. Even an ordinary staff makes a powerful implement which can produce mighty magical effects.
Staves can generally be used as a club in a pinch, although a true fighting staff will be a heavier and more effective weapon. Staves are generally crafted from fine wood
and are often inlaid with minerals or gems, shod with metal, etc. However even a good solid wooden stick of the proper size will do in a pinch.
IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION/
