/IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION
This is a musical instrument of some sort. Instruments of all kinds can potentially be useful in the manipulation of power to create magical effects. Optionally some types of
instrument might have different attributes, being smaller, doing more or less damage, and relying on different abilities. The attributes provided here reflect something like
a generic hand-held string instrument typically used for entertainment purposes. To be useful as an implement an instrument should be of greater than average quality and
further endowed with some enhanced attributes such as special strings. However even basic instruments might suffice in a pinch.
IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION/
