/IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION
The wand is the most classical symbol of magical power amongst all implements. It is a fine tool for the execution of exacting magics. Simple wands are easy enough to craft
and most users can make a passable one with simple tools. The more potent types are finely crafted or made from highly unusual materials using arcane processes.
IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION/
