/IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION
Many practitioners of the magical arts rely on magical books to guide their casting. These are especially useful in the execution of intricate ritual magics and similar
endeavors. Magical tomes often have specific feats and rituals enscribed within them, empowering their owners to new heights of power. A practitioner may scribe a tome. This
requires at least a couple of days of time and requisite materials. Otherwise they might be purchased in certain places.
