/IMPLEMENTDESCRIPTION
Orbs, AKA Crystal balls, are known to be powerful focuses for scrying and divinatory powers, and often act as a means of communication with far places and perhaps even
other worlds. Even an ordinary crystal ball is a useful focus and many of these items are known to possess powerful enchantments. Such implements are not the most easy to
come by, but they can be found in civilized places, etc.
