Knives are common weapons, but they are also often used in the performance of magic. As such most knife implements possess more ornate decorative aspects, or are made of
specific and unusual materials. While such a knife implement may be used in place of a tool or weapon they are generally less robust, being intended more for a symbolic or
ritual purpose. However, in a pinch a finely crafted knife can be used as an implement, and an implement employed as a tool/weapon.
