/SUBSECTION" Tools"/

Tools are general types of equipment which are used for specific purposes. Thus a character might use climbing tools in order to do technical climbing, or carpenter's tools to build things
out of wood. See /REF Proficiencies REF/ for a discussion of being proficient with specific tools. While possession of a specific set of tools may not be required to perform tasks associated
with them, a character who lacks tools entirely may be unable to accomplish anything (IE you can't do woodworking with just your hands) though a limited or improper tool set may still allow
things to be accomplished, possibly with disadvantage.

This is not an exhaustive list of all possible tool sets. Rather what is presented here is a minimum basic toolkit for some common tasks characters are likely to run into. Many others may
exist, and these given may not be sufficient for large or complex tasks.
